### Device Tokens - Register
POST http://localhost:4000/api/device-tokens
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "token": "fcm-or-apns-device-token-here",
  "platform": "android"
}

### Device Tokens - Unregister (on logout)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/device-tokens
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "token": "fcm-or-apns-device-token-here"
}
###